Episode Order: Season 17, Episode 170

And with that, season 17 concludes. The People's Court returns with season 18's inaugural episode sometime in early September, probably the 8th. I, of course, will be there to continue posting episodes. Until then, though, I shall enjoy the break. I will, however, continue to post any missing episodes as they air. Adjourned!

Seed and enjoy!
